import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
        String input = scanner.nextLine();
        String[] numbers = input.split(" ");

        // 计算平均值
        double sum = 0;
        for (String number : numbers) {
            sum += Integer.parseInt(number);
        }
        double avg = sum / numbers.length;

        // 计算方差
        double varianceSum = 0;
        for (String number : numbers) {
            double x = Integer.parseInt(number) - avg;
            varianceSum += x * x;
        }
        double variance = varianceSum / (numbers.length - 1);

        // 输出结果
        System.out.printf("%.2f", variance);
    }
}
```

上述代码会读取一行输入，然后将每个整数提取出来，进行平均值和方差的计算，并输出结果。在这个例子中，输入为"1 1 1 1 1"，输出为"0.00"。请在IDE中运行这段代码，即可得到相应的结果。

