可以使用Java编写程序来实现单链表的重新排序。以下是一个示例代码：

```java
class ListNode {
    int val;
    ListNode next;

    ListNode(int val) {
        this.val = val;
        this.next = null;
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        // 创建单链表
        ListNode head = new ListNode(1);
        head.next = new ListNode(2);
        head.next.next = new ListNode(3);
        head.next.next.next = new ListNode(4);

        // 对单链表重新排序
        reorderList(head);

        // 打印排序后的单链表
        ListNode node = head;
        while (node != null) {
            System.out.print(node.val + " ");
            node = node.next;
        }
    }

    public static void reorderList(ListNode head) {
        if (head == null || head.next == null) {
            return;
        }

        // 找到链表的中间节点
        ListNode slow = head;
        ListNode fast = head;
        while (fast != null && fast.next != null && fast.next.next != null) {
            slow = slow.next;
            fast = fast.next.next;
        }

        // 反转后半部分链表
        ListNode prev = null;
        ListNode curr = slow.next;
        slow.next = null;
        while (curr != null) {
            ListNode next = curr.next;
            curr.next = prev;
            prev = curr;
            curr = next;
        }

        // 合并前半部分链表和反转后的后半部分链表
        ListNode p1 = head;
        ListNode p2 = prev;
        while (p2 != null) {
            ListNode next1 = p1.next;
            ListNode next2 = p2.next;
            p1.next = p2;
            p2.next = next1;
            p1 = next1;
            p2 = next2;
        }
    }
}
```

上述代码会创建一个单链表{1, 2, 3, 4}，然后调用`reorderList`方法对该链表进行重新排序，并打印结果。在这个例子中，输出为"1 4 2 3"。

